Note on source material:

Dante Alighieri's Commedia (c. 1308-1321) is in the public domain.
The persona, place, piece, process, and position files in this folder are
original works by Kai Schlüter. They interpret and adapt themes, structure,
and characters from the Commedia into a KAI Worlds format.
They do not reproduce any translation or critical edition.
No intellectual property in Dante scholarship, translation, or commentary
is claimed.
The KAI HACKS AI architecture - its methods, templates, and structural elements -
is the original contribution claimed under this license.
